            "title": "BIL: 2025 Expected Rates Cuts Slashed, Reassessing The Bond Market",
            "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Interest rate finance and mortgage rates. Wooden block with percentage sign on many level of stack of coin. Financial growth, interest rate increase, inflation, sale price and tax rise concept.\" data-id=\"1933807369\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1933807369/image_1933807369.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Wipada Wipawin</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span>A lot has happened in the past few months within the Treasury market. Recall that the benchmark 10-year yield bottomed out at 3.6% the day before the Fed convened at its September 2024 FOMC meeting. A surprise half-point cut res